Package: fdars
Title: Functional Data Analysis in 'Rust'
Version: 0.3.3
Authors@R: person("Simon", "Müller", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
        "simon.mueller@muon-stat.com")
Description: Functional data analysis tools with a high-performance
        'Rust' backend. Provides methods for functional data
        manipulation, depth computation, distance metrics, regression,
        and statistical testing. Supports both 1D functional data
        (curves) and 2D functional data (surfaces). Methods are
        described in Ramsay and Silverman (2005,
        ISBN:978-0-387-40080-8) "Functional Data Analysis" and Ferraty
        and Vieu (2006, ISBN:978-0-387-30369-7) "Nonparametric
        Functional Data Analysis".
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://sipemu.github.io/fdars-r/,
        https://github.com/sipemu/fdars-r
BugReports: https://github.com/sipemu/fdars-r/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
